description:
Inspector Takeda, Lieutenant Kano, and Sergeant Akiyama of the Nagano Prefectural Police are killed one after another. After observing the crime scenes, Section One Chief Kuroda puts out a BOLO for Inspector Yamato as the murderer of the three men. Conan learns about the man who holed up inside a bank six months prior and Kano`s maiden name from Inspector Morofushi and Detective Yui and closes in on the truth. He has realized who the Woodpocker Society is and the identity of the murderer. Meanwhile, Inspector Saegusa is called by Inspector Yamato to a shack on Mt. Saijo. Approaching from behind him in the culprit holding a stun gun.
Source: crunchyroll
